{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1708-04_76","head":{"value":"[Epitaphe du Pere Mabillon]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", avril 1708 [tome 4], p. 76-78.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"La mort du Pere Mabillon a donné lieu à plusieurs écrits, &amp; ce sçavant Défunt n’a pas manqué d’Epitaphes. Celle qui suit est une Traduction d’une Epitaphe latine."],"quote":{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tu vois sous cette Tombe nuë","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du sçavant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Mabillon","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"les restes precieux ;","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/hi[2]/#"}}]},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De sa seule vertu son ame revêtuë","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Brille maintenant dans les cieux.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par un heureux succés digne de l’entreprise","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des plus Saints de son Ordre il recüeillit les mœurs.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il purgea les écrits de nos sacrez Docteurs","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fut jugé luy-même un Pere de l’Eglise.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/hi/#"}}}]}}}}